{"tid":110993,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[玩具]以為「絕殺」衝場內慶祝 美大學男籃樂極生悲 ...","createTime":"2017-02-07T06:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T09:53:12.000Z","uid":33605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f044ac0d2c3f4c2950214cbfd1698efa3ab27d7","tid":110993,"uid":33605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:17:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Pu1fEsSwLPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPu1fEsSwLPM&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FM2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f8cdbcaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Pu1fEsSwLPM</a><br />\n<br />\n〔體育中心／綜合報導〕NCAA日前一場聖文德大學（St. Bonaventure）對上維吉尼亞聯邦大學（Virginia Commonwealth University）的比賽，聖文德大學球員在終場前0.4秒投進一顆超前三分球，全場球迷嗨翻，還衝進場慶祝，卻被裁判吹技術犯規，雙方進入延長賽，聖文德大學最後不敵對手輸球。<br />\n終場前3.2秒，聖文德大學以63：65落後兩分，該隊從底線發球，莫布里（Matt Mobley）接獲隊友傳球後，投進一顆高難度的三分球，助球隊逆轉比分，聖文德大學球員、以及主場球迷衝進場內慶祝，全場嗨翻。<br />\n但裁判檢視後發現比賽時間還剩下0.4秒，加上聖文德大學球員離開板凳席衝進場內，因此判技術犯規，這也讓維吉尼亞聯邦大學靠罰球進入延長賽。最後聖文德大學在延長賽以77：83輸球。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/41pFU1l0NxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F41pFU1l0NxM&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FM2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=246cecb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/41pFU1l0NxM</a><br />\n<br />\n原文:<a href=\"http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1966325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F1966325&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FM2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=42851be3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F1966325&h=bd9734b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1966325</a>"},{"pid":"0bbf90ec89b2db403d6f380bf48d80f34d659ecb","tid":110993,"uid":33605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a916b76cff30dfb069537e8dbd6c2389f7fb51","tid":110993,"ui